summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting offers from The State of Washington for certain City-owned lands in Rainier Boulevard's Second, Third, Fourth, and Fifth Additions; Bemis Addition, Bradner's Addition; and, Seattle Homestead Association, First Addition for construction of SR-90; authorizing the Mayor to execute a deed and an easement conveying property rights to the State and allocating funds received (SR-90; RW 8405).
